<HEADLINE>
<P>
RECORD RACK: IN BRIEF 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By DENNIS HUNT 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 *** All-4-One, "All-4-One," Blitzz/Atlantic. Tired of all the wanna-be vocal 
groups desecrating doo-wop? Then check out All-4-One's debut album.In 
modern-day doo-wop, this is as good as it gets. The young group's reverence for 
vintage doo-wop is evident on such romantic songs as the glorious remake of "So 
Much in Love," a highlight of this excellent album -- mostly ballads -- 
boasting spine-tingling harmonies. 
</P>
<P>
 New albums are rated on a scale of one star (poor) to four stars (excellent).  
</P>
<P>
 DENNIS HUNT 
