<P>
'HEATHER CHRONICLES' SHORT ON MESSAGE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Re "The Heather Chronicles" by Geraldine Baum (May 5): This was a very long 
article that said nothing. 
</P>
<P>
 They are in "love." Why don't you find something interesting to report about 
and leave these two wonderful people alone? 
</P>
<P>
 JOAN SOCOLA 
</P>
<P>
 Westwood 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Letter to the Editor 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA052994-0101 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 046320 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
May 29, 1994, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Life & Style; Part E; Page 6; Column 1; View Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
