<TEXT>
<P>
 Have a hankering to watch the Supreme Court in action? The court is open to 
the public from 9 a.m. to 4:30 p.m. Monday through Friday, but guided tours 
(led by a court staff member) are available only if they have been arranged in 
advance through your congressional representative's office.The court recommends 
