<HEADLINE>
<P>
TED GUTMAN REMAINS INSPIRATION TO MANY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 * Your "Personal Best" articles do much to uplift us all by focusing on the 
positive people around us. 
</P>
<P>
 I was most happy to see the article by Kay Hwangbo featuring the contributions 
to archeology by longtime Sherman Oaks resident Ted Gutman. 
</P>
<P>
 Additionally, Gutman has been an inspiration to many of us in public service. 
He has been one of those special behind-the-scenes people who encourages and 
helps others to be involved in the issues of our communities. 
</P>
<P>
 LESLEY DEVINE 
</P>
<P>
 Calabasas 
</P>
<P>
 Devine is a member of the Calabasas City Council.  
