r-Marco Greco Brazil 25 1994 Lola-Ford 221.216 33. Scott Goodyear Canada 40 
1994 Lola-Ford 223.817 Field average: 223.270 (record 223.479, 1992) 
</P>
<P>
 r -- rookie 
</P>
</TEXT>
