<DOCNO> LA052994-0317 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 046536 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
May 29, 1994, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 1; Column 3; Foreign Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
