<DATE>
<P>
May 29, 1994, Sunday, Home Edition Correction Appended 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Business; Part D; Page 4; Column 1; Financial Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
