David S. Samuels COB, CEO, P State of the Art Inc. Source: Individual companies 
; Researched by JOHN O'DELL / Los Angeles Times Total Compensation by Firm 
</P>
<P>
 Rockwell heads the list of firms with the largest total executive payrolls. 
