 * Education: Bachelor's degree in criminal justice at Cal State, Los Angeles 
and graduate work in administration at the same university. 
</P>
<P>
 * Career Highlights: During his five years in the Sheriff's Department, Rhodes 
has worked mostly in the jails. He has also served as an instructor at the 
Sheriff's Academy. 
</P>
