 * 
</P>
<P>
 DEMOCRATIC PRIMARY 
</P>
<P>
 Madelene E. Arakelian 
</P>
<P>
 Age: 60 
</P>
<P>
 Occupation: Owner of trash hauling business 
</P>
<P>
 Background: Not available 
</P>
<P>
 Issues: Airport -- Opposes development of airport. Guns -- Favors federal ban. 
Illegal immigrants -- Favors curtailing benefits. Other issues -- Wants to 
redirect current revenue to pay for anti-crime programs without raising new 
revenues; favors tax credits and other economic incentives to help start-up 
businesses. 
</P>
