<P>
 Issues: Airport -- No position on development of airport, but believes land 
should be put up for auction, with bidders offering proposals on best use. Guns 
-- Favors a federal ban only on fully automatic weapons. Illegal immigrants -- 
Introduced bill to end welfare and social services to illegal immigrants. Other 
issues -- Supports repeal of federal laws that mandate appeals for convicted 
criminals and has introduced bill to alter the federal budget process to reduce 
