in 1992; former Eagle Scout and Marine; volunteer with Scouts and youth sports 
leagues. 
</P>
<P>
 Issues: Airport -- Opposes development of airport, believing federal 
government might not follow through on closing the base. Guns -- Opposes 
federal ban. Illegal immigrants -- Opposes curtailing benefits. Other issues -- 
Supports bringing police and military forces "under stronger civilian control"; 
opposes NAFTA. 48th CONGRESS DISTRICT 
</P>
