<HEADLINE>
<P>
DECISION '94; STATE LEGISLATURE: ORANGE COUNTY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The Times sent questionnaires to all candidates for the state Legislature 
asking them about themselves and posing these questions: 
</P>
<P>
 * Do you favor or oppose development of a commercial airport at El Toro Marine 
Corps Air Station? 
</P>
<P>
 * Do you favor or oppose stricter gun control laws? 
</P>
<P>
 * Do you favor or oppose curtailing health care and/or education benefits for 
illegal immigrants? 
</P>
<P>
 * Please list two other issues you feel are important to voters. 
</P>
<P>
 (Only candidates in contested primaries are listed here. For a complete ballot 
see Page V12 .) 67TH ASSEMBLY DISTRICT 
</P>
<P>
 (Cypress, Fountain Valley, Huntington Beach, Seal Beach)  
</P>
