 Occupation: Incumbent assemblywoman 
</P>
<P>
 Background: Former school board member. Elected to Legislature in 1982; 
sponsored successful statewide initiative in 1990 to ban gill nets. 
</P>
<P>
 Issues: Airport -- Favors if surrounding residents not opposed. Guns -- 
Opposes further controls. Illegal immigrants -- Favors curtailment. Other 
issues -- Wants to work to stop crime on campus and drive-by shootings. Also 
wants to try to help business. 
</P>
