Viejo before losing reelection in 1992. Ran unsuccessfully for Mission Viejo 
City Council seat four years ago. 
</P>
<P>
 Issues: "The main reason I decided to run is because it's time for a change. I 
have more experience in a broader area of the law." MUNICIPAL COURT IN 
WESTMINSTER 
