<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
May 29, 1994, Sunday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Special Section; Part V; Page 12; Column 1; Metro Desk 
